query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(k mk t mi_idx) NoMergeJoin(it2 k kt mi mi_idx mk t it1) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS northern_dark_movie
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('revenge',
'fight',
'violence',
'crawl-through-air-shaft')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2001
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '9'
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating'
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'episode'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('English',
'Sweden',
'America',
'Denish',
'Germany',
'Norwegian',
'German',
'Danish',
'USA',
'Canada')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries';
